---
title: Boston Bean, Chorizo and Cheese Loaded Jacky-P with Pickled Onion and Baby Leaves
description: Jacket potatoes aren't just for baked beans and cheese. Our Boston Bean and Cheese Loaded Jacky-P is a smoky, American inspired twist on the humble jacket potato for a comforting weeknight dinner.
